  <條文>
    <條號>Article 21</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The Competent Authority shall collect separate fees for registrations it conducts and tests it performs pursuant to this Act. The fee-charging standards for each category will be prescribed by the Competent Authority.]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
